# Fjarvit — environment variables
#
# Phase 1A reads all content from static JSON in content/cards/ and needs no
# environment variables to run. This file exists so Phase 2 (live API,
# database, scrapers) has a documented place to declare what it needs —
# copy to .env.local and fill in real values once those exist.

# Example for Phase 2 (not yet used):
# DATABASE_URL=
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://fjarvit.com
